nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: An anime-style girl with long auburn hair tied in a high ponytail, held with a red ribbon, wears a glossy red and black futuristic plugsuit marked with the number 02. She stands in profile, focused intently on a red handheld device connected by a cable. Her blue eyes scan the screen as her gloved fingers tap and swipe. Light reflects off the smooth surfaces of her plugsuit, emphasizing its curves and mechanical details. Her hair shifts gently as if in a faint breeze, and the device screen glows softly, casting a faint light onto her face and gloves. The plain gray background keeps full attention on her and her focused posture.
